                        “To create a sustainable and equitable energy future”
                    </blockquote>
                    <p class="lead">
                        Swytch exists to facilitate the transformation of energy markets to meet the demands of our
                        changing world. In today’s electricity markets, consumers depend on a centralized grid that
                        passes on both the cost of generating electricity and the cost of transmitting electricity on
                        the grid. While traditional technologies and markets have required this set up, solar production
                        in one’s home will soon be cheaper than grid transmission costs alone. At the same time, wind
                        and hydro technologies continue to see vast improvements in efficiency and battery technologies
                        are bringing storage costs down precipitously.
                    </p>
                    <p class="lead">
